name: Telemetry Labs, LLC
overview:
Telemetry Labs is a Cloud M2M technology and applications service provider located in Atlanta, Georgia, which offers white label technology solutions and services that deliver next generation web-based remote diagnostic control technologies. It offers technology, application development, application hosting, as well as network and technology management services to those bringing Smart Grid, Smart Infrastructure and Smart Services to the market.

Telemetry Labs provides every component within the M2M value chain, as well as complete end-to-end solutions. From analysis and planning, to integration, certification, and technical and user support, it seeks to assist customers achieve success in the market place by using technology to empower their business operations.
